``legitimate'' source of on-line commerce, but still lags behind
pornography. We list Internet sites not so much that sell on line,
but that provide information that can help plan vacations. By HARRY
SHATTUCK.
</P>
<P>
   BUSINESS/FINANCE (``f'' category)
</P>
<P>
   CAREER-COLUMN (San Francisco) _ If you look back at Steve
Young's years with the San Francisco 49ers, you can learn a lot
about your own career, even if you don't know the difference
between a safety blitz and a cheese blintz. Here are a few things
you can learn from it. By DAVE MURPHY.
</P>
