   &UR; (EDITORS: IN THE WAKE OF SYRIAN PRESIDENT HAFEZ AL-ASSAD'S SUDDEN
DEATH OVER THE WEEKEND AND HIS BURIAL TODAY (TUESDAY), THE NEW YORK
