<P>
   &UR; INTERNATIONAL (i) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   IRELAND-GUERIN (Dublin) _ Four years after muckracking Irish
reporter Veronica Guerin was murdered, a movie about her life is
due. But the problems she exposed have gotten worse. By Kevin
Cullen. 1100 words.
