Explorer Sport Trac is a rig for gearheads. That's not gearheads as
in folks who like nothing more than to tear into the mechanical
intricacies of what they drive. It's gearheads who like their
vehicles to carry lots of stuff: skis, snowboards, bikes, kayaks,
garden tools, manure, lumber, groceries. The vehicle features an
optional extension that flips onto an open tailgate and adds two
feet to the 50-inch bed. (Farnk O'Brien/The Boston Globe)
